extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Fire and Storm!
Unleash a storm of battle with the Legendary Pokemon of the seas: Lugia! With the fiery wings of Moltres and the mystic flame of Delphox, you'll burn through opposition in a flash with the Sky Guardian theme deck. Light it up!

Contents:
• 1 60-card preconstructed deck
• Damage counters
• 1 coin
